name: OCKDataSeries
desc: A single group of data that the chart plots.

items.name: init(dataPoints: [CGPoint], title: String, size: CGFloat, color: UIColor?)
items.desc: Creates a new data series, that can be passed to a chart to be plotted using a single solid color.

items.name: init(dataPoints: [CGPoint], title: String, gradientStartColor: UIColor, gradientEndColor: UIColor, size: CGFloat)
items.desc: Creates a new data series, that can be passed to a chart and plotted using a gradient color scheme.

items.name: init(values: [CGFloat], title: String, size: CGFloat, color: UIColor?)
items.desc: Creates a new data series, that can be passed to a chart to be plotted using a single, solid color.

items.name: init(values: [CGFloat], title: String, gradientStartColor: UIColor, gradientEndColor: UIColor, size: CGFloat)
items.desc: Creates a new data series, that can be passed to a chart and plotted using a gradient color scheme.

items.name: var dataPoints: [CGPoint]
items.desc: An array of points in plot space Cartesian coordinates.

items.name: var title: String
items.desc: A title the chart uses to display data series in the plot legend.

items.name: var accessibilityLabels: [String]
items.desc: An array of strings the data series uses for accessibility labels.

items.name: var gradientStartColor: UIColor?
items.desc: The first of two colors that the gradient uses when plotting the data.

items.name: var gradientEndColor: UIColor?
items.desc: The second of two colors that the gradient uses when plotting the data.

items.name: var size: CGFloat
items.desc: A size that specifies how large this data series appears on the plot.
